### AI Chat - base vars
@host = http://127.0.0.1:13101
@contentType = application/json;charset=UTF-8

### enable model list
GET {{host}}/aiEngine/api/v1/ai/models/enable
Accept: application/json

### 1) Non-stream chat
POST {{host}}/aiEngine/api/v1/ai/execution/chat
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Accept: application/json

{
  "provider": 2,
  "model": "qwen-math-turbo",
  "messages": [
    {
      "role": "USER",
      "content": "张三的岗位是什么？"
    }
  ],
  "options": {
    "temperature": 0.7,
    "topP": 0.8,
    "maxTokens": 256,
    "timeoutMs": 30000
  },
  "meta": {
    "traceId": "local-http-chat-001",
    "scene": "manual-http-test"
  },
  "ext": {
    "kbId": "w05enpcxa4"
  }
}

### 2) Stream chat (SSE)
POST {{host}}/api/v1/ai/execution/chat/stream
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Accept: text/event-stream;charset=UTF-8

{
  "provider": "DASHSCOPE",
  "model": "qwen-math-turbo",
  "messages": [
    {
      "role": "USER",
      "content": "请分三点介绍上海"
    }
  ],
  "options": {
    "temperature": 0.6,
    "topP": 0.9,
    "maxTokens": 512,
    "timeoutMs": 30000
  },
  "meta": {
    "traceId": "local-http-stream-001",
    "scene": "manual-http-test"
  }
}
